### Component 3: Asset Pipeline Scripts

#### [NEW] [fetch-images-mythos.ts](file:///c:/Users/ADMIN/Desktop/AInewsvideo/scripts/fetch-images-mythos.ts)
Tavily-powered image search script. Fetches 3 images per scene (30 total) for 3-second cut cycling. Follows the established `fetch-images-tavily.ts` pattern.

#### [NEW] [generate-voiceover-mythos.ts](file:///c:/Users/ADMIN/Desktop/AInewsvideo/scripts/generate-voiceover-mythos.ts)
ElevenLabs TTS with `/with-timestamps` endpoint. Generates MP3 + JSON sidecar per scene (word-level timing). Follows `generate-voiceover-apr14.ts` pattern.

---

### Component 4: Remotion Composition

#### [NEW] [MythosShort.tsx](file:///c:/Users/ADMIN/Desktop/AInewsvideo/src/components/MythosShort.tsx)
Main composition component. Built on the proven `NewsShortV2.tsx` template with:
- **TransitionSeries** with fade transitions between scenes
- **Word-synced captions** from ElevenLabs JSON sidecars  
- **3-second cycling backgrounds** with Ken Burns pan/zoom
- **Network header** bar (customized for "AI DEEP DIVE" branding)
- **Audio waveform** visualization bound to voiceover
- **Grain + particles + light leaks** (always-on visual density)
- **Scene tag badges** with corresponding emojis
- **Source attribution** bars per scene
- **Segmented progress bar** at bottom

**Hype & Retention Protocol compliance:**
- `spring({ stiffness: 350, damping: 20 })` — snap entry for all elements
- `Easing.bezier(0.1, 1, 0, 1)` — hostile easing, no linear
- ≥4 hard visual changes in first 90 frames (3 seconds)
- No static frame survives >30 frames
- Kinetic typography with word-level entrance animations

#### [MODIFY] [Root.tsx](file:///c:/Users/ADMIN/Desktop/AInewsvideo/src/Root.tsx)
Register the new `mythos-short` composition with `calculateMetadata` for dynamic duration.

