## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
1. `npx tsx scripts/generate-voiceover-mythos.ts` — Confirm 10 MP3 + 10 JSON files written
2. `npx tsx scripts/fetch-images-mythos.ts` — Confirm image downloads from Tavily
3. `npm run dev` — Open Remotion Studio, preview `mythos-short` composition
4. Verify total duration ≈ 2700 frames (90s × 30fps)
5. Confirm word-synced captions align with audio playback
6. Confirm ≥4 visual changes in first 3 seconds

### Manual Verification
- Preview full video in Remotion Studio at 1× speed
- Verify all 10 scene transitions are smooth  
- Confirm text readability on mobile (1080×1920 safe zone)
- Audio-visual sync check on scene boundaries
